name: mixed_jrcmca
source:
def mixed_jrcmca(x, y):
    t1 = jnp.log(jnp.abs(x) + 1e-6)
    t2 = jnp.power(jnp.abs(t1), jnp.abs(y) % 3 + 1)
    t3 = jnp.sum(t2)
    return t3
